channel.title: Help with a private server
channel.description:
this isnt about programming a server or anything. but i quit rsps's about 1 year ago and i used to play on a really good server. i cant remember the name so i will describe it and will someone try to tell me the name. someones gotta play it.
i remember u would spawn in varrock then u could thieve from either stalls or people (cant remember which) and u wld get p-hats or tokens for the well or cannon shots for the multi cannon. there was a well where youd drop int okens and get like santa armour or jester outfits. u cld get a multi cannon easily at the blacksmith in varrack by the middle. you could go to a spot where the helldogs shld be and kill corp. tell me the name please. oh and there was alot of customs.
